WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:04.000
the city of Gaziantep near the Syrian border.

00:04.000 --> 00:07.000
Ameer is doing his school homework.

00:07.000 --> 00:10.000
It's in Turkish, and despite speaking Arabic at home,

00:10.000 --> 00:13.000
it's his strongest language he tells us.

00:13.000 --> 00:16.000
I'm born in Syria, so my identity is Syrian,

00:16.000 --> 00:19.000
but I lived here for nine years,

00:19.000 --> 00:21.000
and it feels like I'm more Turkish.

00:21.000 --> 00:24.000
Yes, I want to go back, like to visit it,

00:24.000 --> 00:25.000
but not like to live.

00:25.000 --> 00:29.000
I want to live here because of my educational purposes,

00:29.000 --> 00:30.000
so I can...

